sentences.english: Around 4-6% of elderly people have experienced some form of maltreatment at home.

sentences.english: In some extend, I am not a hypercritical person about food.

sentences.english: I think that he says that it's kind of implied consent.

sentences.english: There seems to be some majestic primeval connection between a man and a mountain.

sentences.english: There are reports of microbes surviving for much longer in a kind of suspended animation.
